{"id":558453,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/【图说天朝】惨无人道的动物炼狱/","date":"2017-05-08T07:16:11Z","modified":"2017-05-08T07:16:11Z","title":"【图说天朝】惨无人道的动物炼狱","content":"<p>@默潭噢：海口动物园绝对是我去过最惨无人道的动物炼狱，爬虫馆一半的蛇直接在玻璃箱里成了蛇干。黄额和缅甸烂的只剩下爪子。蟒蛇，巨蜥，娃娃鱼是泡在福尔马林里的尸体。鳄鱼池水又浅又脏漂满了矿泉水瓶。哺乳动物刻板行为严重，老虎笼子空间很小，挤了两只孟加拉虎。黑熊在原地不停地点头。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558461\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsxrk4c9j30qo0qoaek-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558462\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/005H4gsaly1ffdsytcuuij30qo0qojvb-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 6